{"type":"miscellaneous","title":"Hardy Saddle","summaries":["The <b>Hardy Saddle</b> is a <linked>mount</linked>-summoning item. When used, it summons a <b>Turtle Mount</b> that can swim and has increased movement speed in <linked>liquids</linked> (<abbr title=\"51 miles per hour (as measured by the Stopwatch item) or 37.5 tiles per second\" class=\"nowrap\"><span class=\"gameText\">51 mph</span></abbr> maximum), but reduced movement speed (<abbr title=\"26 miles per hour (as measured by the Stopwatch item) or 18.75 tiles per second\" class=\"nowrap\"><span class=\"gameText\">26 mph</span></abbr> maximum) and <linked>jump reach</linked> (3.53 tiles maximum) on land. It can be found in <linked>Golden Crates</linked> with a <span class=\"chance\"><s>9.33*</s>7/75 (9.33%)</span> chance, and in <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Titanium Crates</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span> with a <span class=\"chance\"><s>6.53*</s>49/750 (6.53%)</span> chance."],"statistics":{"Use time":"20 <span class=\"usetime\">(Very fast)</span>","Tooltip":"<i><span class=\"gameText\">Summons a rideable Turtle mount</span></i>","Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\"><linked>[img:Rarity level: 8]</linked></span>","Sell":"<span class=\"coin\" title=\"5 Gold Coins\" data-sort-value=\"50000\"><span class=\"gc\">5</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">1 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{}}